item.title: 【Interviews / TV shows / Others】PACK - Dolby Labs - DCX Functional Testing & Tuning
item.description:
This is official Dolby Atmos DCX Functional Testing and Tuning

It was collected from diffrent sources. Then I tested and packed in matroska container.
I didn't repack or modified original sources, just packed.

All files were tested on Sony Bravia A90J, A83J (Google TV) and Samsung Soundbar HW-Q930B.

Is there any problem, please let me know in comments.
